lines.text:
[to a soldier with a red dot on his forehead]
What's on your forehead?

[pointing her laserscoped gun at them]
What are you boys doing?

[points his gun at her]
Drop the gun!
Well looks like we've got a Mexican standoff here.
So you think I'm scared of you, huh? Bitch!
Hell yes I think you're afraid of me.
